If you need help with joining our server please visit www.tagcraftmc.com/firsttime

--Extra Info--

Our launcher allows you to select different versions of Minecraft as well as mods. We have a tutorial on our website informing you how to add your own mods, or you can use our patching system that allows you to download and run an installer that added the popular SMP mods for you. (Rei's minimap, Optifine, MacroMod, TabbyChat, Forge, ect)

If you're in a nostalgic mood, we have also got an auto patcher that installs Minecraft version 1.4.5 &gt; 1.6.4.

Our client also allows you to dedicate the desired amount of ram you want to your client.

